Concordance Table: H4 to I3.1

Source: R/data.R
H4_I31.Rd

H4_I31

Format

A data frame with 5,205 rows and 4 variables:

HS 2012 Product Code

Harmonised System HS 2012 (H4) Product code.

HS 2012 Product Description

Harmonised System HS 2012 (H4) Product description.

ISIC Revision 3.1 Product Code

International Standard Industrial Classification ISIC Rev. 3.1 (I31) Product code.

ISIC Revision 3.1 Product Description

International Standard Industrial Classification ISIC Rev. 3.1 (I31) Product code.

Source

https://unstats.un.org/unsd/trade/classifications/bec.asp
